Hi Robyn!  The <#1279085616247869451> channel is used to approve numbers to be added to the call list!  Every now and then, a staff member will post a link that needs a lot of people to just click the buttons to do the approvals, and then they will say "check again" when they are finished.  That's it!  Do not worry about any kind of logging in or out for this.

When the next link is posted, the staff will ping again, and anyone who sees it online at the time will be in there clicking until it's done.  They can get done fast!
